item.title: I cant make my guy a admin
item.dc:creator: @Marz Marz
item.description:
@Marz wrote:

Just delete your current file then log on and wait until it writes your file into Characters… then go into your eric.txt or whatever your username is and then change Player Rights = 0 to Player Rights = 3 for owner or 2 for admin

You might not see your crown and you’ll need the owner crown fix, just do a search for that
